'''Taskserver''', also known as '''taskd''',  is an open-source server daemon that allows users to sync their task data between multiple devices.


==Security==

Security is provided through public-key encryption, and knowledge of a shared key.


==Supported Clients==

Taskserver currently supports [[Taskwarrior]] 2.3.0


==History==

Development began in September 2012


